{"tid":419912,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A][機槍撚] Star Trigger［迷失宇宙］刷出美麗人生","createTime":"2017-10-01T02:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T15:47:10.000Z","uid":137898,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"359dd4e8a0e52a1d7864794fe4b12bfe15b7f961","tid":419912,"uid":137898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"官網：[url]http://www.startrigger. <a href=\"http://rekoo.co.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frekoo.co.jp&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2FviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=549337d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rekoo.co.jp</a> [/url]<br />\nWiki. : <a href=\"https://startrigger.gamerch.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstartrigger.gamerch.com&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2FviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=af7c9acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://startrigger.gamerch.com</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/TTqiNCZhmVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTTqiNCZhmVs&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2FviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f20bfe0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TTqiNCZhmVs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/093053_6d83874cbe6af8998d8e2a0b38ead647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F093053_6d83874cbe6af8998d8e2a0b38ead647.jpg&h=a1425b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA）首抽教學<br />\n1）直接完成首章六關卡有2700石送，用來直接十抽<br />\n1.1) 抽到UR留餘下石等下次十抽<br />\n1.2）抽唔到UR用餘下石再抽<br />\n1.3）再抽唔到UR重新開game ，start畫面左下角禁初期化再來過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095808_e3e37a5a87730fa14077db2d3b693d18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095808_e3e37a5a87730fa14077db2d3b693d18.jpg&h=06e1af1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB) 系統介紹<br />\n攻擊：角色輸出能力，由武器攻擊和角色自身攻擊组成，主要由武器提供。<br />\n防禦：角色抵抗輸出能力，主要由裝備、角色升級、角色强化等提供。<br />\n韌性：角色抵抗額外暴擊傷害的能力，主要裝備、角色升級、角色强化等提供。<br />\n命中：角色有效攻擊的成功率，主要由武器提供。<br />\n閃避：角色防止有效攻擊的成功率，主要由裝備、角色升级、角色强化等提供。<br />\n暴擊：角色產生額外傷害的能力，主要由武器提供。<br />\n平衡：角色进行攻擊時，控制傷害波動範圍的能力，越高表示越有可能打出上限傷害，主要由武器提供。<br />\n穿甲：角色进行攻擊時，無視對方防禦的能力，越高表示能無視更多的防禦进行攻擊，主要由武器提供。<br />\n暴傷：角色產生額外暴擊傷害值的倍率範圍，等級越高，表示額外暴擊傷害倍率越高。<br />\n<br />\nC) 武器介紹<br />\n近擊武器、雙槍武器、霰彈槍武器、狙擊武器、重型武器<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095735_c28a5f8c1014ade09e68a13893810fe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095735_c28a5f8c1014ade09e68a13893810fe1.jpg&h=b595908b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095736_a149525f26c4cb2079093f974d4c6fa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095736_a149525f26c4cb2079093f974d4c6fa8.jpg&h=90e140b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095736_d7cb5d8bf2143f64bb460350efceb604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095736_d7cb5d8bf2143f64bb460350efceb604.jpg&h=01681987&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095737_d7cb5d8bf2143f64bb460350efceb604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095737_d7cb5d8bf2143f64bb460350efceb604.jpg&h=e97f8926&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/095737_8ee741d01cc018124653e50992190d18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F095737_8ee741d01cc018124653e50992190d18.jpg&h=9b141718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/100720_074566107fdd5d27d0bc937a89a317c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F201